				"description": "Retrieve transaction status for the given UTI.\n\nReturns a 400 if no transaction exists for the given UTI.\n\nReturns a 200 with the transaction status if the transaction is in progress:\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"statusDescription\": \"Transaction started\"\n}\n\n ```\n\nReturns a 200 with the transaction result, if the transaction is finished:\n\n``` json\n{\n    \"appName\": \"4D4320435245444954\",\n    \"applicationId\": \"A0000000041010\",\n    \"authCode\": \"\",\n    \"cardholderReceipt\": \"Custom receipt JSON\",\n    \"cardholderVerificationMethod\": \"CVM_NO_CVM\",\n    \"currencyCode\": \"352\",\n    \"dccAmount\": 0,\n    \"dccCommissionAmount\": 0,\n    \"dccExchangeRate\": 0.0,\n    \"dccTransaction\": false,\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"isCustomCardData\": false,\n    \"merchantId\": \"800573916121001\",\n    \"merchantReceipt\": \"Custom receipt JSON\",\n    \"messageId\": 162,\n    \"primaryAccountNumber\": \"541333******0036\",\n    \"signature\": false,\n    \"statuses\": \"[\\\"Transaction started\\\",\\\"Contactless card read\\\",\\\"Transaction declined\\\",\\\"Transaction finished\\\"]\",\n    \"terminalId\": \"34550576\",\n    \"tipAmount\": 0,\n    \"totalAmount\": \"500000\",\n    \"transApproved\": false,\n    \"transCancelled\": false,\n    \"transactionDate\": \"Dec 12, 2023 10:45:13 AM\",\n    \"transactionResponse\": \"97\",\n    \"transactionSource\": \"PICC\",\n    \"transactionType\": \"SALE\",\n    \"uti\": \"fcdaa106-e046-403f-ae12-5fc145c68130\",\n    \"voided\": false\n}\n\n ```"
			},
